Package org.anchoranalysis.feature.input

Interface FeatureInput

All Known Subinterfaces:
FeatureInputParams, FeatureInputWithResolution
All Known Implementing Classes:
FeatureInputAllMemo, FeatureInputEnergy, FeatureInputHistogram, FeatureInputMark, FeatureInputMarkCollection, FeatureInputNull, FeatureInputObjectCollection, FeatureInputPairMemo, FeatureInputPairObjects, FeatureInputResults, FeatureInputSingleMemo, FeatureInputSingleObject, FeatureInputStack
public interface FeatureInput
A single input used for feature-calculation to produce a result.

i.e. when this object passed into an appropriate feature, a double result is created for it
